#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/emails/billing-trial-converting.email.tsx
msgid "If Twenty is working for you, you're all set — there's nothing to do. If it's not the right fit, you can cancel in one click before then and you won't be charged."
msgstr "Si Twenty us funciona, ja està tot preparat — no heu de fer res. Si no és el producte adequat, la podeu cancel·lar amb un sol clic abans d'aquesta data i no se us cobrarà res."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/emails/password-update-notify.email.tsx
msgid "If you did not initiate this change, please contact your workspace owner immediately."
msgstr "Si no has iniciat aquest canvi, si us plau contacta amb el propietari de l'espai de treball immediatament."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/emails/billing-trial-ending.email.tsx
msgid "If you do nothing, we'll pause your workspace and keep your data safe for {dataRetentionDays} days in case you change your mind — no card will be charged."
msgstr "Si no feu res, posarem en pausa el vostre espai de treball i mantindrem les vostres dades segures durant {dataRetentionDays} dies en cas que canvieu d'opinió — no es carregarà cap targeta."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/emails/clean-suspended-workspace.email.tsx
msgid "If you'd ever like to give Twenty another try, you can start a fresh workspace in minutes — we'd love to have you back."
msgstr "Si mai voleu tornar a provar Twenty, podeu iniciar un espai de treball nou en pocs minuts — ens encantaria tenir-vos de nou."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/components/WhatIsTwenty.tsx
msgid "It's a CRM, a software to help businesses manage their customer data and relationships efficiently."
msgstr "És un CRM, un programari per ajudar les empreses a gestionar les seves dades de clients i relacions de manera eficient."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/emails/clean-suspended-workspace.email.tsx
msgid "Its data has been removed and can no longer be recovered."
msgstr "Les seves dades s'han suprimit i ja no es poden recuperar."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/emails/send-invite-link.email.tsx
msgid "Join your team on Twenty"
msgstr "Uneix-te al teu equip a Twenty"

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/emails/billing-subscription-renewing.email.tsx
msgid "Just so it's never a surprise, here's a heads up about your annual plan."
msgstr "Perquè no sigui mai una sorpresa, aquí teniu un avís sobre el vostre pla anual."

#. js-lingui-explicit-id
#: src/emails/billing-subscription-renewing.email.tsx
#: src/emails/billing-trial-converting.email.tsx
